"BlockID: 1235
Call context: bidWithPlugin,_bid
None
REF_161 -> reward.nftKind
TMP_177 = CONVERT REF_161 to uint256
TMP_178 = TMP_177 << 128
TMP_179 = 1 << 255
TMP_180 = TMP_178 | TMP_179
REF_162 -> reward.tokenIndex
TMP_181 = TMP_180 | REF_162
tokenId := TMP_181
TMP_182 = CONVERT this to address
HIGH_LEVEL_CALL, dest:token1155(BlockchainCutiesERC1155Interface), function:safeTransferFrom, arguments:['TMP_182', 'purchaser', 'tokenId', '1', '']  "
